465
00:25:11,280 --> 00:25:12,640
Apa pun? Siapa pun?

466
00:25:13,160 --> 00:25:14,600
Apa dia mengenalmu?

467
00:25:16,080 --> 00:25:18,160
Morris, bisakah kau perbesar wanita itu?

468
00:25:18,240 --> 00:25:20,080
Tanganku bekerja secepat mungkin.

469
00:25:20,600 --> 00:25:21,920
MEDAN ELEKTROMAGNETIK

470
00:25:22,960 --> 00:25:26,320
Dia menudingmu,
