471
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:27,720
Ada apa pun di sana?

472
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:30,840
Kolonel Chidozie, kembalilah ke posisimu.

473
00:25:30,920 --> 00:25:32,360
Lihat apa ada sesuatu di sana.

474
00:25:32,440 --> 00:25:35,680
- Dokter, kau melarang kami bergerak.
